com.invensense.cubequat

Class Global

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.invensense.cubequat.Global

  • public class Global
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a Global class that is primarily intended to provide a bridge between the sensor values that are shared between different classes and activities. A better alternative of class could be Listener pattern.
